            <thetext>fixed in r20436

The decorator cache did not grow indefinitely. After short usage it is usually saturated and does not grow any further. However the pool has been refactored:

- The number of decorators of each type is now limited
- Only decorators defined in a decorator theme are pooled because sharing of manually instantiated decorators may lead to memory leaks
